  "body": "### Description\n\nIt would be nice if there was a \"Running tests in continuous integration\" section in the [Testing your application guide](https://quarkus.io/guides/getting-started-testing). \r\n\r\nThis section read by people who are setting up the tests in their Quarkus app. They are probably interested in setting up the tests in continuous integration as well. \r\n\r\nThis is often the case on testing guides from other frameworks, they show you how to run the tests locally, and by the end of the guide you will set them up for CI as well.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
